### Admin Users API

### List users
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users?limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Create user (invite by email)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Staff User",
  "email": "staff@example.com",
  "role": "Staff"
}

###

### Promote / demote role
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/staff%40example.com/role
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "Admin"
}

###

### Disable user
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/staff%40example.com/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "enabled": false
}

###

### Enable user
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/staff%40example.com/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "enabled": true
}

###

### Send password reset
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/staff%40example.com/reset-password
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
